---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import mrbeastHero from "@/assets/work/mrbeast_hero.png";
---
<Layout
  title="Beast Mode Banking — MoneyLion × Beast Games"
  description="From #33 to #1 most-downloaded finance app in a single day. Ian Luna, ACD Copy at WITHIN, 2024–25."
  sceneName="EXT. HIGHWAY — BILLBOARD 01"
  frameNumber="003"
>
  <main id="main" class="case">
    <div class="content">
      <a href="/work" class="back-link-floating" aria-label="Back to the booth">
        <span class="back-glyph" aria-hidden="true">←</span>
        <span class="back-text">Back to the booth</span>
      </a>

      <!-- HERO PANEL — shared-element morph destination. The BEAST MODE BANKING billboard
           in /work has view-transition-name: case-study-mrbeast; this panel matches it.
           Browser handles the morph. -->
      <section class="case-hero-billboard" style="view-transition-name: case-study-mrbeast;">
        <Image src={mrbeastHero}
          alt="A weathered roadside billboard at night reading BEAST MODE BANKING in chunky red commercial typography. Painted on green-and-cream wood. Lit by a single sodium-vapor pole lamp. Deep indigo sky, atmospheric haze, distant telephone-pole silhouettes."
          widths={[768, 1280, 1536, 2048, 2560]} sizes="100vw"
          formats={["avif", "webp"]} loading="eager" fetchpriority="high"
          class="hero-photo" />
        <div class="hero-titlecard">
          <h1 class="billboard-title">BEAST MODE BANKING</h1>
          <p class="billboard-meta">MoneyLion × Beast Games · Amazon Prime · 2024 — 2025</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <header class="case-head">
        <div class="case-meta">
          <span class="meta-pill">Featured · 01</span>
          <span class="meta-divider" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
          <span class="meta-pill">2024 — 2025</span>
        </div>
        <p class="case-deck">A finance app meets the biggest show on streaming. The integration that didn't feel like an integration.</p>
        <dl class="credits">
          <div class="credit"><dt>Brand</dt><dd>MoneyLion × Beast Games (Amazon Prime)</dd></div>
          <div class="credit"><dt>Agency</dt><dd>WITHIN</dd></div>
          <div class="credit"><dt>Role</dt><dd>Associate Creative Director, Copy</dd></div>
          <div class="credit"><dt>Year</dt><dd>2024 – 2025</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </header>

      <section class="kpi-strip">
        <article class="kpi">
          <span class="kpi-num">#33 → #1</span>
          <span class="kpi-label">Most-downloaded finance app, in a single day</span>
        </article>
        <article class="kpi">
          <span class="kpi-num">1B+</span>
          <span class="kpi-label">Brand impressions across the campaign</span>
        </article>
        <article class="kpi">
          <span class="kpi-num">3M+</span>
          <span class="kpi-label">Giveaway entries</span>
        </article>
        <article class="kpi">
          <span class="kpi-num">Record</span>
          <span class="kpi-label">Audience engagement on MoneyLion's social channels</span>
        </article>
      </section>

      <section class="prose">
        <h2 class="h2">The setup</h2>
        <p>MoneyLion wanted attention. Beast Games was Amazon Prime's most-watched series of the year. The brief was simple in shape and impossible in execution: integrate a finance app into a Mr. Beast world without the integration feeling like the integration.</p>
        <p>Don't bolt MoneyLion onto Beast Games. Make MoneyLion feel like it was always part of the show.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="prose">
        <h2 class="h2">The tagline</h2>
        <blockquote class="hero-line">
          <p>Beast Mode Banking.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </section>

      <section class="prose">
        <h2 class="h2">Out-of-home & launch boards</h2>
        <ul class="lines">
          <li>WIN A MILLION. THE APP HELPS YOU SAVE ONE.</li>
          <li>1,000 CONTESTANTS. ONE WINNER. AN APP THAT WORKS FOR ALL OF THEM.</li>
          <li>MONEYLION. NOW THE OFFICIAL SPONSOR OF YOUR LIFE NOT SUCKING.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="prose">
        <h2 class="h2">Push notifications — reactive, real-time</h2>
        <ul class="lines">
          <li>Beast just dropped $50K. You haven't logged in today.</li>
          <li>Episode 4 dropped. So did 700 contestants. You're still in.</li>
          <li>Your free Beast Games entry expires at midnight. Banks close earlier than that.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="prose">
        <h2 class="h2">In-app messaging — post-install</h2>
        <ul class="lines">
          <li>Welcome. You're now playing for keeps.</li>
          <li>Beast played for a million. Play for the next one.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="prose">
        <h2 class="h2">TV spot — :30 (excerpt)</h2>
        <pre class="script">EXT. STADIUM PARKING LOT, DAY.

Jimmy walks toward camera, holding a black duffel.

JIMMY:    This is a million dollars.

He drops it. It thuds. He keeps walking.

JIMMY (O.S.):  MoneyLion is giving one away.

CUT TO: hand opening the app. MoneyLion logo, Beast Games chyron.

JIMMY (O.S.):  You don't need a million dollars to start. You need a minute.

END FRAME: BEAST MODE BANKING. MoneyLion.</pre>
      </section>

      <section class="prose">
        <h2 class="h2">What I did</h2>
        <ul class="bulleted">
          <li>Helped develop the irreverent, punchy tone that merged the Beast universe with MoneyLion's brand.</li>
          <li>Delivered high-energy copy across TV, social, OOH, and in-app channels.</li>
          <li>Co-wrote scripted media spots and promotional content for TV, digital, and social.</li>
          <li>Wrote reactive copy in real time, riding audience buzz and engagement spikes.</li>
          <li>Shaped pre-launch hype messaging.</li>
          <li>Wrote attention-grabbing push notifications and in-app messaging.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <footer class="case-foot">
        <a href="/work" class="foot-link" data-astro-prefetch>
          <span class="foot-glyph" aria-hidden="true">←</span>
          <span>Back to all work</span>
        </a>
        <span class="foot-divider" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
        <span class="foot-note">More case studies in preparation.</span>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .case-hero-billboard {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 21 / 9;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .hero-photo {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover; object-position: center center;
    display: block;
  }
  .hero-titlecard {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom,
      rgba(10, 9, 8, 0.0) 0%,
      rgba(10, 9, 8, 0.0) 50%,
      rgba(10, 9, 8, 0.65) 100%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .billboard-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6.5vw, 5.5rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--color-neon-work);
    text-shadow: 0 0 28px rgba(82, 240, 90, 0.55),
                 0 0 8px rgba(82, 240, 90, 0.7),
                 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
  }
  .billboard-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    opacity: 0.85;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Shared-element morph DESTINATION — matches the billboard in /work */
  
  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .case-hero-billboard { aspect-ratio: 4 / 3; }
  }
  
  

  .back-link-floating {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5em;
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-muted); text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6); padding-top: var(--space-4);
  }
  .back-link-floating:hover { color: var(--color-cream); }

  /* Older .back-link rule still used elsewhere; keep harmless */

  .case {
    min-height: calc(100vh - var(--frame-bar-h) * 2);
    margin-top: var(--frame-bar-h);
    padding: var(--space-16) var(--space-6) var(--space-32);
    background: var(--color-silhouette);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .content { width: 100%; max-width: 760px; }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5em;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .back-link:hover { color: var(--color-cream); }

  .case-meta {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }
  .meta-pill {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-3xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-marquee-warm);
  }
  .meta-divider { color: var(--color-muted); opacity: 0.5; }

  .case-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display, "Fraunces", "Newsreader", serif);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5.5rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-5);
  }
  .case-deck {
    font-family: var(--font-body, "Lexend", sans-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.45;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    opacity: 0.85;
    max-width: 50ch;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-10);
  }
  .credits {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin: 0;
    padding: var(--space-6) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-cream) 14%, transparent);
    border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-cream) 14%, transparent);
  }
  .credit dt {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-3xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.3em;
  }
  .credit dd {
    font-family: var(--font-body, "Lexend", sans-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.35;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .kpi-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-1);
    margin: var(--space-12) 0;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-neon-work) 6%, transparent);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-neon-work) 28%, transparent);
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: var(--space-6);
  }
  .kpi { padding: var(--space-3); }
  .kpi-num {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-display, "Fraunces", "Newsreader", serif);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(var(--text-2xl), 3.5vw, var(--text-4xl));
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--color-neon-work);
    margin-bottom: 0.3em;
  }
  .kpi-label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    opacity: 0.7;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .prose { margin: var(--space-12) 0; }
  .h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-marquee-warm);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-5);
  }
  .prose p {
    font-family: var(--font-body, "Lexend", sans-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .hero-line {
    margin: var(--space-6) 0;
    padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-6);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-neon-work);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-neon-work) 4%, transparent);
  }
  .hero-line p {
    font-family: var(--font-display, "Fraunces", "Newsreader", serif);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(var(--text-2xl), 4vw, var(--text-4xl));
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .lines {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .lines li {
    font-family: var(--font-body, "Lexend", sans-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.45;
    padding: var(--space-3) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-cream) 6%, transparent);
    color: var(--color-cream);
  }
  .lines li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .script {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.6;
    background: rgba(15, 27, 46, 0.5);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-cream) 12%, transparent);
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: var(--space-6);
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    overflow-x: auto;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .bulleted {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .bulleted li {
    font-family: var(--font-body, "Lexend", sans-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.55;
    padding: var(--space-2) 0 var(--space-2) var(--space-5);
    position: relative;
  }
  .bulleted li::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 1.1em;
    width: 0.8em;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--color-neon-work);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .case-foot {
    margin-top: var(--space-20);
    padding-top: var(--space-8);
    border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-cream) 14%, transparent);
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.7em;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-2xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }
  .foot-link {
    color: var(--color-cream);
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5em;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .foot-link:hover { opacity: 0.7; }
  .foot-divider { opacity: 0.4; }
</style>
